title: Super Spacious 1BD in Ditmas Park**Private Balcony**No Fee**Gym**Roof-Deck
posting_body: ['Welcome to 1111 Foster Avenue!', 'This unit features double-pained windows and generous amounts of closet space and is equipped with a suite of Stainless-Steel LG Appliances including a refrigerator, range, dishwasher and microwave.', 'Enjoy the convenience of a split system for heating and cooling with individual thermostats for added efficiency.', 'No brokers fee!', 'Private balcony!', 'Great Neighborhood!', 'Distinguished Amenities Include:-Laundry Room on every floor-A fully equipped Fitness Center-Package Room-Bicycle Storage-Optional on-site Parking and EV charging stations-Private Outdoor Spaces & Sundeck', 'Situated in Ditmas Park, and on the border of Kensington and Midwood, this building is conveniently located just 4 short blocks from the B&Q train lines and is near multiple local and express buses so you can have easy access to Manhattan and to South Brooklyn.', 'Only a few blocks from Newkirk Ave and Cortelyou Rd, you will find an array of well-regarded restaurants, bars, cafes, Flatbush co-op, a farmer’s market, Brooklyn ARTery and countless other shops.']
